On 12/8/2018 at 10:20 AM, flinkymeatball said:

The issue am having is that my game crashes in the middle of startup, I am trying to find out what mod(s) caused it, ill link the output log below~

https://drive.google.com/file/d/1AcC06OMwxefKFEGkZ0BRACWtUCrsEPKX/view?usp=sharing

Probably not the correct log since it shows no crash and a couple of scene switches in game. The linked log is from KSP 1.2.2, I guess you don't know yet, that the log location changed in KSP 1.4.+ (or you actually play on 1.2.2 but than the log still doesn't show any crashes).

The correct log for KSP 1.4.+ is located here: %USERPROFILE%\AppData\LocalLow\Squad\Kerbal Space Program\output_log.txt

Edited December 9, 2018 by 4x4cheesecake
The log says you have two different versions of USI Tools and RetractableLiftingSurface. Also the Near Future stuff is for 1.5.x.

BTW am running the newest version (1.5)

well I did kinda find a fix, I got rid of B9 and OPT and it runs again, it must be something to do with them

And also the correct Output log, https://drive.google.com/file/d/1AcC06OMwxefKFEGkZ0BRACWtUCrsEPKX/view?usp=sharing
